---
title: 231. Power of Two
tags:
        - LeetCode刷题笔记
        - 教程
---
`(n & (n-1)) == 0`用来判断是否是2的幂，前提n>0
```c
bool isPowerOfTwo(int n){
    bool result = false;
    if(n > 0 && (n & (n - 1)) == 0){//判断符号(==)比&的比较级高
        result = true;
    }
    // printf("%d\n", n & (n - 1));
    return result;
}
```
